search_results.title: Roman Krznaric - Author of History for Tomorrow
search_results.snippet: Roman Krznaric's books include History for Tomorrow, The Good Ancestor, What The Rich Don't Tell The Poor, Carpe Diem Regained, Empathy, and The Wonderbox.

search_results.title: Author and Public Philosopher - Roman Krznaric
search_results.snippet: Roman Krznaric is a public philosopher who writes about the power of ideas to change society. His books include The Good Ancestor and Empathy.

search_results.title: Ediberto Roman
search_results.snippet: Ediberto Roman is an American legal scholar working as a professor of law at the Florida International University College of Law.
